  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When ever you attack an target, regardless if it is a hit or a miss, you may choose to mark that target. While a target is mark, it takes a –2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn. If a marked enemy that is adjacent to you shifts, or makes an attack that does not include you as a target, you may make a @UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.example_powers.Item.3sPbAZBvQCrYAByQ]{Melee Basic Attack} against that target as part of an immediate interrupt.</p>",
